FBIS4-33810 "drlat113_b_94014" FBIS-LAT-94-113 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 Barbados Haiti Noailles Warns of `Disinformation Trap' Noailles Warns of `Disinformation Trap' FL1106001394 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio in French 1030 GMT 10 Jun 94 FL1106001394 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio French BFN [Text] The Interior and National Defense Ministry has issued a protest note. Joseph Willio Noailles, interior and national defense minister, has formally deplored the media's malicious exploitation of his statements. The protest is in response to reports that Minister Noailles called the government illegitimate. He vehemently denies saying the infamous words, which he said were put in his mouth while he was in the Republic's Senate. Noailles asks the public to remain calm and to avoid the disinformation trap set for the government.
